<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome</title>

    <style>
        .content {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #F2F2F2;
        }
        .header {
            margin: 0px 48px 0px 48px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 0px 24px 0px;
        }

        .header-logo img {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
        }

        .header-text {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }
        .header > img {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .header-text .title {
            padding-bottom: 7px;
        }

        .middle {
            border: 1px solid #DADAEB;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            max-width: 568px;
            margin: 0px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .yellow-border {
            border: 1px solid #FFD201;
        }

        .content-box {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 24px 32px 32px 32px;
        }

        .middle-logo {
            margin: 0px 0px 16px 0px;
        }

        img {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
        }

        .rectangle {
            background: #DADAEB;
            max-width: 504px;
            height: 1px;
            margin: 0px 48px 0px 48px;
        }

        .rectangle-middle {
            margin: 0px 32px 0px 32px;
        }

        .rectangle-box {
            max-width: 568px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #DADAEB;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .middle-text {
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }

        .title {
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .bottom {
            max-width: 568px;
            margin: 24px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .button-rectangle {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 56px;
            background: #1CD18B;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .button-rectangle img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .person {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 0px 16px 32px;
        }

        .arrow {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 32px 16px 0px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .text {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top:14px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .bottom-text {
            max-width: 504px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            margin: 16px 32px 0px 32px;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }

        .footer {
            max-width: 568px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 31px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            color: #9999AD;
        }

        .footer img {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;

        }

        .footer .text-box {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 0px 32px 0px 32px;
        }

        .text-box .big {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #9999AD;
        }

        .text-box .general {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .small-font {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .medium-font-14 {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .medium-font-16 {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 22px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .title-font {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 22px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;

        }

        .green {
            color: #1CD18B;
        }

        .text-box-general {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 24px 48px 32px 48px;
            color: #2D363D;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 0px !important;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="content">

        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-logo">
                <img src="{{ logo }}" alt="Frizbee Logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="header-text medium-font-14">
                <div class="title title-font bold green">
                    It’s awesome to have you here!
                </div>
                <div>
                    We built Frizbee to create a friendly and practical network for anybody with a passion. Here are a few ways to get you started in the Hobby Stadium.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="middle">

            <div class="content-box">
                <div class="middle-logo">
                    <img src="{{ group1 }}" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="middle-text">
                    <div class="title title-font bold">
                        Join a group or create your own
                    </div>
                    <div class="medium-font-14">
                        Meet everybody and invite more friends through our public and private groups.
                        Find the best community for you, using hobby categories and tags to narrow it down to a perfect match.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rectangle rectangle-middle"></div>

            <div class="content-box">
                <div class="middle-logo">
                    <img src="{{ group2 }}" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="middle-text">
                    <div class="title title-font bold">
                        Start a video session
                    </div>
                    <div class="medium-font-14">
                        Find somebody inspiring to help you start or improve on your hobbies.
                        Spread the craft and share your knowledge, teaching fellow enthusiasts.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="bottom">

            <div class="button-rectangle">
                <div class="person">
                    <img src="{{ person }}" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="text medium-font-16">
                    Join Frizbee
                </div>
                <div class="arrow">
                    <img src="{{ arrow }}" alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom-text small-font">
                Become an official Frizbeean by creating your very own Frizbee account. This is your ticket to the best features of our hobbylicious app.
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="rectangle"></div>

        <div class="footer">

            <div class="text-box small-font">
                <div class="big medium-font-16">
                    And this is just the beginning of our beautiful friendship!
                </div>
                <div class="general">
                    Help us become better and nicer for you, by sharing any & all your thoughts, ideas and reviews. We’ll be waiting  for them by
                    <a href="#" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none !important;">support@frizbee.app</a>
                    and our in-app feedback form.
                </div>
                <div class="general" style="margin-top: 16px;">
                    We’ll always have hobbies. Promise!
                </div>
                <div class="general signature">
                    the Frizbee <img src="{{ heart }}" alt=""  /> Bunch
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>


    </div>

</body>
</html>